1. Installed NVM using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited and reopened the terminal

3. Loaded NVM manually using:
   export NVM_DIR="$HOME/.nvm"
   [ -s "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" ] && \. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh"

4. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
   nvm install 20.16.0

5. Created project directory:
   mkdir -p ~/alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss

6. Installed latest SASS version using:
   npm install sass

7. Verified SASS version:
   npx sass --version



